00:33:08.920 --> 00:33:11.080
One of them is
that you see people

00:33:11.080 --> 00:33:14.540
trying to keep up with the
next rung just above them.

00:33:14.540 --> 00:33:17.530
So there is this sort of these
consumption patterns start

00:33:17.530 --> 00:33:19.840
to get ratcheted up because
