00:33:31.540 --> 00:33:34.340
that just were not available
30, 40, 50 years ago.

00:33:34.340 --> 00:33:34.840
Right?

00:33:34.840 --> 00:33:38.020
So we all have credit cards, but
also just the ability to get--

00:33:38.020 --> 00:33:42.550
to have access to so
