00:33:55.840 --> 00:33:57.464
that mortgage or I
can pay off that car

00:33:57.464 --> 00:33:59.930
or whatever, then that can
be a good way of closing

00:33:59.930 --> 00:34:01.510
a short term gap.

00:34:01.510 --> 00:34:06.490
But in a world where people
are trying to sort of keep up,

00:34:06.490 --> 00:34:09.639
or where they feel that
