00:34:19.360 --> 00:34:24.070
it's based on tax
dollars in communities,

00:34:24.070 --> 00:34:26.480
so that richer communities
have better schools.

00:34:26.480 --> 00:34:26.980
Right?

00:34:26.980 --> 00:34:29.800
That creates enormous
pressure especially

00:34:29.800 --> 00:34:32.320
in an era where it's
harder and harder

00:34:32.320 --> 00:34:33.732
