00:34:38.710 --> 00:34:41.199
and then you've got these
debt instruments, mortgages,

00:34:41.199 --> 00:34:44.840
and other that make it a lot
easier for families to do so.

00:34:44.840 --> 00:34:46.540
Of course we've
learned, and we're

00:34:46.540 --> 00:34:49.750
all I believe older
than the age of eight

00:34:49.750 --> 00:34:52.199
